AntiSamy plugin for Play framework
==================================


# Usage

1.  name your policy file to antisamy.xml and put it under conf/ of your application directory
2.  invoke AntiSamyPlugin.filter() to filter dirty string input, you'll get a clean string output (the degree of cleanliness depends on your policy file)
    String clean = AntiSamyPlugin.filter(dirty);


# Reference

